- Azure VM RDP Troubleshooting

This scenario simulates an Azure support case where a customer cannot connect to their Windows VM using RDP.

Skills Demonstrated:
- Azure CLI diagnostics
- Network Security Group (NSG) configuration
- VM extension and PowerShell automation
- Root cause analysis and resolution

 Tools Used:
- `az vm get-instance-view`
- `az network nsg rule create`
- `az vm run-command invoke`
